full_text:
To add a blog to your website, you really just need three things:

1.  a folder to hold all of your individual posts
2. a listing page
3. blog posts! 

Figuring out where those live inside your project can be confusing, but students found this diagram helpful: (2/5) https://t.co/I9lQNinJZz
